        <summary><![CDATA[GreenTown Curacao meets member of Parliament, Andre Bosman, member of the VVD, the largest political party in The Netherland. Mr. Bosman knew about the pollution on Curacao, but was not aware of the Asphalt Lake and the low economic significance of the current refinery. Mr. Bosman will help GreenTown to find paths in the European Union and will keep a close eye on the decision making process regarding the Isla refinery.]]></summary>
