        <summary><![CDATA[Today, GreenTown had a more than three hours informal discussion with Alex Rosaria, the leader of Partido PAIS, one of the political parties that form the Government of Curaçao.   ]]></summary>
        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Today, GreenTown had a more than three hours informal discussion with Alex Rosaria, the leader of Partido PAIS, one of the political parties that form the Government of Curaçao.   GreenTown presented its vision, its network, its GreenTown Parties concept and its plans to create a better future for Curaçao. All participants listened very well and exchanged ideas how to create more economic growth, employment and sustainability on Curaçao.  It was a very inspiring meeting, and it will be continued.</p>]]></bodyText>
